      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，采纳的回答本质上是一条评论。所以讨论可以有采纳的回答，同时评论本身也可以被标记为被采纳。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discussion",
        "Accepted Answer",
        "Comment"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
